Expert Wordpress and Shopify Developer

Adelaide, Australia - 9:05 pm local time
I'm an expert Wordpress and Shopify developer with five years of experience in web development. Strong background in developing all kinds of websites and applications for small to big clients. I will help you transform your personal or business concept into a successful WordPress or Shopify based website.

WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU:
- Custom themes build from the ground up, optimized for performance
- Adjusting premium themes to your needs with optimization for performance
- Analysis and optimizing your website for performance (Fast Page Load)
- API Integrations for Paypal, Stripe, YouTube, Twitter, Facebook, and others

WHAT YOU GET:
- A website/online store that is easy to manage you'll be able to change its behaviour or options with no coding knowledge required
- If you're new to Wordpress or Shopify, I'll show you how to work with it
- An extremely high-quality source code that is clean, simple and maintainable
- Quick response time

WHY ME:
I focus on the goal you want to achieve. I make sure I understand and can implement all your requirements and suggested applicable improvements. I always make sure that my finished product is high quality and well tested, and the source code is clean, simple, and maintainable.

Send me a note with a bit about your company, your track record, and your project. If it seems like a good fit, well schedule a call to talk.

Steps for completing your project

Rashmi works on your project following the steps below.

Gathering requirements
